[{"Id": 1012753, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "On the order of the Abbaside Caliph, Musa al-Haadi nearly a hundred men from the progeny of Fatimah (s) are martyred and buried at this place. Their Ziyarat is same as that of the off-springs of Imams (a). It is as follows…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Yeh woh maqaam hai jahan khaleefa’e Abbasi, Moosa Al-Haadi ke hukm se saadaat’e Fatema (s) mein se taqreeban 100 afraad ko shaheed kiya gaya tha yeh sab yahin dafn hai. Unke liye woh ziyarat padhna chahiye jo aulad’e Aimma (a) ke liye waarid huwi hai…", "UrduDescription": "یہ وہ مقام ہے جہاں خلیفۂ عبّاسی موسی الحادی کے حکم سے ساداتِ فاطمہؑ میں سے تقریبًا ۱۰۰ افراد کو شہید کیا گیا تھا، یہ سب یہیں دفن ہیں۔ ان کے لئے وہ زیارت پڑھنا چاہیئے جو أولاد ائمہؑ کے لئے وارد ہوئی ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign1